title: A discombobulating ride with an aerobatics pilot
text: > Sports A discombobulating ride with an aerobatics pilot Associated Press sports writer John Marshall, front, flies upside-down with Red Bull plane racing pilot Kirby Chambliss on a flight near the pilot's home Wednesday, April 29, 2015, in Eloy, Ariz. Practicing three times a day, seven days a week, Chambliss turned himself into a five-time U.S. national aerobatics champion and was one of the founding pilots in the Red Bull Air Races when the series began in 2003. (AP Photo/Ross D. Franklin)
